{"id":15658,"date":"2024-05-22T08:00:20","date_gmt":"2024-05-22T08:00:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/?p=15658"},"modified":"2025-04-09T10:16:31","modified_gmt":"2025-04-09T10:16:31","slug":"6valley-v14-6-dynamic-email-templates-and-seller-friendly-upgrades","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/blog\/6valley-v14-6-dynamic-email-templates-and-seller-friendly-upgrades\/","title":{"rendered":"6Valley v14.6: Dynamic Emails and Seller Friendly Upgrades\u00a0"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Good news for all the existing and new 6Valley <a href=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/\">Multi Vendor eCommerce CMS<\/a> users. <a href=\"https:\/\/codecanyon.net\/item\/6valley-multivendor-ecommerce-complete-ecommerce-mobile-app-web-and-admin-panel\/31448597\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">6Valley<\/a> has been upgraded to version 14.6, bringing a host of new features and improvements to enhance your experience.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features List of 6Valley v14.6:<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Custom sorting for all lists from the admin panel<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Dynamic email templates for all users<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Low stock warnings with popup notifications<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Selected product checkout with remaining items in the cart<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Improved Excel design for vendor export data<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Guest user account creation on the checkout page<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Enhanced seller registration page<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Separate &#8216;Buy Now&#8217; checkout without removing other cart items<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s a closer look at what awaits you in this update:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Custom sorting for all lists from the admin panel<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins can now set the view of &#8211; Brand, Category, Vendor List, Featured Products, New Arrival Products, Top Vendor, Category Wise Product List, Top Rated Products, Best Selling Products, Products List (Search Bar), Vendor Product List from the \u201cPriority Setup\u201d tab.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This feature allows better management of different lists throughout the platform. It makes navigation easier and access to important information faster.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"540\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/1-custom-sorting-admin-panel.webp\" alt=\"Admin panel Custom sorting List\" class=\"wp-image-15659\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/1-custom-sorting-admin-panel.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/1-custom-sorting-admin-panel-300x179.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/1-custom-sorting-admin-panel-768x457.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;Business Setup&gt;Business Settings&gt;Priority Setup&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can scroll through the&nbsp; \u201cPriority Setup\u201d tab to manually control the view for each list. Click on the \u201cCustom Sorting List\u201d toggle to sort the section in your way. Click \u201cSave\u201d to update the settings. Otherwise, each of the lists will be viewed in the platform based on the rule of \u201c Use Default Sorting List\u201d toggles.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/blog\/multi-vendor-ecommerce-marketplace-website\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/blog\/multi-vendor-ecommerce-marketplace-website\/\">How to Build a Multi Vendor eCommerce Website with 6Valley<\/a><\/strong><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>On the customer\u2019s end, they will be able to view the changes for each list based on the admin\u2019s rules. Below is the change made for the \u201cBrands\u201d to get sorted alphabetically from Z to A \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"506\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/custom-sorting-customer-view.webp\" alt=\"Brands\" class=\"wp-image-15660\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/custom-sorting-customer-view.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/custom-sorting-customer-view-300x167.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/custom-sorting-customer-view-768x428.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>User Website&gt;Brands<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dynamic email templates for all users<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you can send more relevant and personalized emails from the dynamic email templates for each user of the system. This upgrade introduces customizable email templates for all types of emails sent from the system. You can now personalize the look and content of your emails, making communication more engaging and professional.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the details of each template for individual users of the system:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"553\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/3-admin-email-template.webp\" alt=\"Get email on order recieved\" class=\"wp-image-15661\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/3-admin-email-template.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/3-admin-email-template-300x183.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/3-admin-email-template-768x468.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;System Setup&gt;Email Template (Admin mail template)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"550\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/4-vendor-email-template.webp\" alt=\"Get email on registration\" class=\"wp-image-15662\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/4-vendor-email-template.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/4-vendor-email-template-300x182.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/4-vendor-email-template-768x466.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;System Setup&gt;Email Template (Vendor mail template)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"549\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/5-customer-email-template.webp\" alt=\"Get email on order page\" class=\"wp-image-15663\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/5-customer-email-template.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/5-customer-email-template-300x182.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/5-customer-email-template-768x465.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;System Setup&gt;Email Template (Customer mail template)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"547\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/6-deliveryman-email-template.webp\" alt=\"Reset Password Verification\" class=\"wp-image-15664\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/6-deliveryman-email-template.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/6-deliveryman-email-template-300x181.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/6-deliveryman-email-template-768x463.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;System Setup&gt;Email Template (Delivery Man mail template)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Low stock warnings with popup notifications<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Both admins and vendors will receive instant popup notifications when stock levels are low. This ensures that they can quickly restock items and avoid potential sales interruptions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mainly 3 different types of notifications will be sent based on the number of products in stock:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>100+ Product Count:<\/strong> When the total count of products with low stock is over 100, the notification informs the admin and seller that an insufficient quantity of products is available.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2 to 100 Coun<\/strong><strong>t:<\/strong> This warns both sellers and admins by mentioning the number of products that are approaching low stock levels in between this range.<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1 product: <\/strong>For this, the notification notifies the admin and seller that this particular product is low on stock by mentioning the product name.<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is how the different popup notifications will look from both the admin panel and seller panel \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"388\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/7-Pop-up-notification-1.webp\" alt=\"Low stock warnings with popup notifications 1\" class=\"wp-image-15665\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/7-Pop-up-notification-1.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/7-Pop-up-notification-1-300x128.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/7-Pop-up-notification-1-768x329.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"326\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/8-Pop-up-notification-2.webp\" alt=\"Low stock warnings with popup notifications 2\" class=\"wp-image-15666\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/8-Pop-up-notification-2.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/8-Pop-up-notification-2-300x108.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/8-Pop-up-notification-2-768x276.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"328\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/9-Pop-up-notification-3.webp\" alt=\"Low stock warnings with popup notifications 3\" class=\"wp-image-15667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/9-Pop-up-notification-3.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/9-Pop-up-notification-3-300x108.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/9-Pop-up-notification-3-768x278.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, if you\u2019re using the demo 6Valley admin and seller panel, you will get notified about the data reset time interval \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"460\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/10-demo-reset-notification-on-admin-panel.webp\" alt=\"Maintenance Mode\" class=\"wp-image-15668\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/10-demo-reset-notification-on-admin-panel.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/10-demo-reset-notification-on-admin-panel-300x152.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/10-demo-reset-notification-on-admin-panel-768x390.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> 6Valley Demo Admin Panel<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Selected product checkout with remaining items in the cart<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Customers can now choose to check out selected items while keeping the rest of their cart intact. This means they can complete purchases without losing other items they were considering.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"540\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/11-selected-product-checkout-with-remaining-items-in-the-cart.webp\" alt=\"Selected product checkout\" class=\"wp-image-15669\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/11-selected-product-checkout-with-remaining-items-in-the-cart.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/11-selected-product-checkout-with-remaining-items-in-the-cart-300x179.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/11-selected-product-checkout-with-remaining-items-in-the-cart-768x457.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> User Website&gt;My Cart (Checkout Page)&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Improved Excel design for vendor export data&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Excel export options for all order-related data for vendors have been redesigned for better clarity and usability. This improvement helps vendors easily analyze and manage their data.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"549\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/12-seller-panel-excel-export.webp\" alt=\"Improved Excel design for vendor export data\u00a0\" class=\"wp-image-15670\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/12-seller-panel-excel-export.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/12-seller-panel-excel-export-300x182.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/12-seller-panel-excel-export-768x465.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>Seller Panel&gt;Order Management&gt;Orders&gt;All<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After downloading they will get an improved view like this \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"461\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/13-improved-excel-design.webp\" alt=\"Order List\" class=\"wp-image-15671\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/13-improved-excel-design.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/13-improved-excel-design-300x152.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/13-improved-excel-design-768x390.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Guest user account creation on the checkout page<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Guests can now create an account directly from the checkout page with the data they&#8217;ve already entered. This simplifies the registration process and encourages more users to sign up.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>They just have to check the \u201cCreate an account with the above info\u201d box and give a password to register their account.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"488\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/14-guest-user-account-creation-on-the-checkout-page.webp\" alt=\"Guest user account creation\" class=\"wp-image-15672\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/14-guest-user-account-creation-on-the-checkout-page.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/14-guest-user-account-creation-on-the-checkout-page-300x161.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/14-guest-user-account-creation-on-the-checkout-page-768x413.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>User Website&gt;My Cart (Checkout Page)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Enhanced Seller Registration Page<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The seller registration page has been updated to be more informative and user-friendly. New sellers will find it easier to sign up and understand the requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From the User Website, sellers can find the option to join as a vendor and start selling. Check the images below showcasing the user-friendly and easy-to-navigate vendor registration page &#8211;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"1572\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/become-a-vendor-page.webp\" alt=\"Enhanced Seller Registration Page\" class=\"wp-image-15682\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/become-a-vendor-page.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/become-a-vendor-page-173x300.webp 173w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/become-a-vendor-page-591x1024.webp 591w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/become-a-vendor-page-768x1331.webp 768w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/become-a-vendor-page-886x1536.webp 886w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>User Website&gt;Vendor Zone&gt;Become A Vendor&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Separate &#8216;Buy Now&#8217; checkout without removing other cart items<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The &#8216;Buy Now&#8217; option allows customers to purchase a single item immediately without affecting the rest of their shopping cart. This makes the buying process more flexible and convenient.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Customers can buy additional items instantly, even if they already have other items in their cart.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"907\" height=\"447\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/18-separate-buy-now.webp\" alt=\"checkout without removing other cart items\" class=\"wp-image-15676\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/18-separate-buy-now.webp 907w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/18-separate-buy-now-300x148.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/18-separate-buy-now-768x378.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 907px) 100vw, 907px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>User Website&gt;Item Details<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking &#8220;Buy Now&#8221; directs them to the checkout page to complete the order without removing anything from the existing cart.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Other Improvements<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are more significant improvements from version 14.6 that ensure a seamless and optimized user experience &#8211;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Migrated Firebase push notification API to HTTP v1<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Various fixes and improvements in web panels and app<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Compatibility with Flutter SDK 3.19.6<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>That\u2019s all from this version. We are constantly evolving! Don\u2019t miss a beat &#8211; stay tuned for the latest news and updates.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Good news for all the existing and new 6Valley Multi Vendor eCommerce CMS users. 6Valley has been upgraded to version 14.6, bringing a host of new features and improvements to enhance your experience.&nbsp; Features List of 6Valley v14.6:&nbsp; \u2699\ufe0f Custom sorting for all lists from the admin panel \u2699\ufe0f Dynamic email templates for all users &#8230; <a title=\"6Valley v14.6: Dynamic Emails and Seller Friendly Upgrades\u00a0\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/blog\/6valley-v14-6-dynamic-email-templates-and-seller-friendly-upgrades\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about 6Valley v14.6: Dynamic Emails and Seller Friendly Upgrades\u00a0\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":15,"featured_media":15677,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[211],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-15658","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-update"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15658","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/15"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15658"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15658\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15677"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15658"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15658"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15658"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}